                <div>
                    <h3>Progressive disclosure</h3>
                    <p>
                        Even data should use the layering concept, turning huge pools of content, into digestible and digestible chunks of information. Information should be categorized and grouped, creating different levels of detail that can be dug into, allowing the user to get invaluable insights.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            <article class="grid-2-2 align-center">
                <div>
                    <h3>Iconic data visualization</h3>
                    <p>
                        Data visualization is an extremely powerful tool, allowing users to get actionable insights on their data. Our focus should be on delivering valuable information, following a graphically refined and character rich design language, that will be clearly perceived as <b>Ericsson</b>.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <video autoplay loop muted playsinline aria-label="An animation showing how Ericsson data viz looks like" style="width: 70%;">
